Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: ADFlib - shared library.
 This is a a free, portable and open implementation of the Amiga filesystem.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

